10 6 2 234 Team spokesman Tim Mead confirmed Sunday the Angels have withdrawn their offer and are ``out of the Mark Teixeira derby.''
10 6 3 235 The team made its offer, reportedly worth about US$160 million, during the winter meetings in Las Vegas earlier this month.
10 6 4 236 The Red Sox said last week that they ``are not going to be a factor'' in signing the 28-year-old Maryland native. 
