10 6 6 238 The Angels obtained Teixeira from the Atlanta Braves in late July. 
10 6 7 239 Playing in a combined 157 games with the Angels and Braves, Teixeira had 33 homers and 121 RBIs along with a career-best .308 average.
10 7 1 240 So as things turn out, apparently there are teams in Major League Baseball not named the New York Yankees who are willing to spend money this winter.
