12 17 4 468 The Indian warship, which was escorting merchant ships some 13 miles away, responded to the distress call.
12 17 5 469 They launched marine commandos on an armed helicopter and altered course to confront the pirates.
12 17 6 470 The bandits lost nerve on seeing the helicopter and the warships and attempted to flee
