12 6 7 590 The mother vessel, a 10-metre craft called Salahaddin, had some catch stocked in it to give the impression that it was a fishing vessel.
12 6 8 591 The Mysore intercepted the mother vessel and fired ahead of it to prevent the pirates from getting away.
12 6 9 592 Sources said the marine commandos had sighted pirates carrying rocket-propelled grenade launchers and automatic weapons.
