16 1 7 948 Police earlier confirmed that Escalante was shot in his head from behind and may never have seen his murderer.
16 1 8 949 Bratton asked for the public's help in providing additional information now that the suspects' names were made public.
16 1 9 950 The city had offered a $75,000 in the case, and the county Board of Supervisors added another $20,000 to that pot.
