18 12 33 1015 At a weekend news conference, city police spokesman Const. 
18 12 34 1016 Tim Fanning said Kirkpatrick had been let go from TallGrass on Thursday.
18 12 35 1017 Fanning didn't know how long the suspect had worked at the business.
18 12 36 1018 The other people at the office party were able to escape without injury, Fanning said.
18 12 37 1019 ``The shock was tremendous but all the other people in the business - and a dozen other people who were there for a Christmas party - managed to get out safely,'' Fanning said.
18 12 38 1020 The shocked party-goers were put on buses and taken to police headquarters where witness statements were taken, he said.
