28 2 1 2631 Mark Felt, the mysterious ``Deep Throat'' source who <MENTION CHAIN="3">helped</MENTION> Washington Post reporters Bob Woodward and Carl Bernstein <MENTION CHAIN="4">crack</MENTION> the Watergate <MENTION CHAIN="2">scandal</MENTION> that <MENTION CHAIN="5">brought</MENTION> down President Richard Nixon, has <MENTION CHAIN="1">died</MENTION> at age 95.
