30 11 1 3352 Damaged undersea cables disrupting service
30 11 2 3353 Parts of Asia, the Middle East, and Europe <MENTION CHAIN="1">experienced</MENTION> Internet and telephone <MENTION CHAIN="3">outages</MENTION> Friday when three undersea cables between Italy and Egypt in the Mediterranean Sea were <MENTION CHAIN="2">damaged</MENTION>.
