30 12 2 3367 Internet and telephone communications between the Middle East and Europe were <MENTION CHAIN="1">disrupted</MENTION> after three submarine cables between Italy and Egypt in the Mediterranean Sea were <MENTION CHAIN="2">damaged</MENTION>.
30 12 3 3368 The <MENTION CHAIN="3">failures</MENTION> <MENTION CHAIN="1">cut</MENTION> the flow of ``data of various kinds'' between Europe and the Middle East, and there's no timeframe for when communications will be <MENTION CHAIN="7">restored</MENTION>, said Sanjeev Gaur, director of assurance at Reliance Globalcom Ltd. in India.
