30 7 1 3478 Severed cable disrupts net access
30 7 2 3479 Internet and phone communications between Europe, the Middle East, and Asia have been seriously <MENTION CHAIN="1">disrupted</MENTION> after submarine cables were <MENTION CHAIN="2">severed</MENTION>.
30 7 3 3480 It is thought the FLAG FEA, SMW4, and SMW3 lines, near the Alexandria cable station in Egypt, have all been <MENTION CHAIN="1">cut</MENTION>.
