31 5 6 3742 Hansbrough now has 2,301.
31 5 7 3743 Hansbrough needed 9 points coming in and <MENTION CHAIN="5">set</MENTION> the record with a bank <MENTION CHAIN="17">shot</MENTION> over two defenders with 7 minutes 41 seconds to go.
31 5 8 3744 After the game, the university showed a video montage of Hansbrough's career highlights, and he briefly addressed the crowd.
