37 6 6 4464 ``I've instructed emergency steps be taken to help our brothers and to restore power and other vital utilities,'' Yudhoyono said.
37 6 7 4465 Among the dead was a 10-year-old girl, identified as Yolanda Mandofi, whose head was crushed, said local hospital director Hengky Tewu.
