4 9 5 4946 To me, she'll always be the kooky, naive Christian portrayed by Gretchen Mol in The Notorious Bettie Page.
4 9 6 4947 But more than that, she was trailblazer for sexy unconventional women everywhere.
4 9 7 4948 Without her, the Suicide Girls wouldn't exist, although it's questionable whether that's a real loss.
4 9 8 4949 I chose the above picture to memorialize her because everyone loves monkeys.
4 9 9 4950 RIP Bettie!
4 9 10 4951 I'll drink a martini and listen to a Cramps song in your memory tonight.
