40 10 9 4977 Through the use of advanced chemistry, intelligent monitoring, adaptive charging technology, and a multi-cell design that Apple claims achieves three times the industry standard in battery life.
40 10 10 4978 The new battery system will deliver eight hours on a single charge and can be recharged up to 1,000 times in a single lifespan.
