5 9 2 6083 The 76ers have a record of 9-14 and had been expected to be a playoff team in the Eastern Conference.
5 9 3 6084 With its acquisition of free agent Elton Brand the lineup seemed to be become more solid especially in the middle.
5 9 4 6085 But Brand has not found his rhythm in the offense and his numbers have been disappointing.
