5 9 7 6088 With Brand's arrival the hope turned into what fans thought was a reality.
5 9 8 6089 Never before in NBA history have coaches fallen this early in the season in such numbers.
5 9 9 6090 Veteran players know all too well that the security their union has fought for has created an imbalance of power on teams that don't have a proven winner in the coaching seat.
5 9 10 6091 When a player is paid tens of millions of dollars by a franchise, he is in the driver's seat and if it comes down to a contest between that player and a coach who hasn't won a title or hasn't won a title in a long while, it's not hard to know who has to go.
